### Getting Started - Sample HTTP Requests
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension or as curl reference

@apiUrl = http://localhost:8080
@sourceUrl = http://localhost:9000/sources/products-source/events

### Health Check
GET {{apiUrl}}/health

### Get Source Status
GET {{apiUrl}}/sources/products-source

### Get Query Status
GET {{apiUrl}}/queries/expensive-products

### Get Query Results
GET {{apiUrl}}/queries/expensive-products/results

### Add New Product (Direct Format)
POST {{sourceUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operation": "insert",
  "element": {
    "type": "node",
    "id": "prod-009",
    "labels": ["Product"],
    "properties": {
      "id": "prod-009",
      "name": "Gaming Mouse",
      "price": 69.99,
      "category": "Electronics",
      "in_stock": true
    }
  }
}

